  "description": "<i>Fuffy</i> is a Yahtzee game written in GFA Basic for 1-4 players. In every turn the player may roll the dice three times and in every roll select which dice to keep so that he/she can combine them to get the best possible score. As in the original Yahtzee-game there are 13 combinations that gives points.  The game comes with a statistics part where the player can see dice and player stats.",
